<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Behind the Apron - Cafe Chefs</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f1e5;
            color: #5c3d2e;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #8b5e3b;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 30px auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .chef-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 320px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .chef-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .chef-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .chef-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #8b5e3b;
        }

        .chef-role {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #5c3d2e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .chef-quote {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #5c3d2e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>Behind the Apron: Stories from Our Cafe Chefs</header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="chef-card">
            <img class="chef-img" src="https://assets.cntraveller.in/photos/60ba16548c5b530e12127511/16:9/w_1024%2Cc_limit/RRAAA-S2_9-1366x768.jpg" alt="Chef ranveer">
            <div class="chef-name">Chef Ranveer Brar</div>
            <div class="chef-role">The Breakfast Artisan</div>
            <div class="chef-quote">
                "Mornings at the café are my favorite. There’s something magical about the scent of fresh pastries and hot lattes. Seeing a customer’s smile after the first bite makes those early mornings worth it."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chef-card">
            <img class="chef-img" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTV12Q3nVyvX9cgpLcEKifTalGx19iuUL70ZtWm97XhaAZJGJ92JlTHc1MpOcUViyV3FOk&usqp=CAU" alt="Chef Maria">
            <div class="chef-name">Chef Garima Arora </div>
            <div class="chef-role">The Queen of Seasonal Specials</div>
            <div class="chef-quote">
                "I find inspiration in the seasons. Each drink and dish should tell a story of the time of year. Experimenting with new flavors and seeing what our customers love most is my favorite part."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chef-card">
            <img class="chef-img" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTt1A_duyAXQ2HJFxORyis2mZucRbbCpPG6BkpD-_L70H4quRDmMs_-dQ4q0IQUXPLc8hg&usqp=CAU" alt="Chef Liam">
            <div class="chef-name">Chef Vikas Khanna</div>
            <div class="chef-role">The Pastry Perfectionist</div>
            <div class="chef-quote">
                "Baking is both an art and a science. I love crafting pastries that pair perfectly with coffee. My favorite? The seasonal scones we bake fresh every morning."
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
